description:
Makeup artist Stephanie Flor, founder of Around The World Beauty, shares life lessons and beauty discoveries from Peru, Ecuador, India, Japan, Morocco, and other spots. Plus, she spills backstage secrets from New York Fashion Week. Before that, we discuss the new "lo-fi facial" (get into it!) and the FDA’s latest proposed sunscreen guidelines (and the Environmental Working Group’s surprising response to them).
